人的见识也有点比同层次的中国年轻人低的感觉，不知道知乎的各位怎么看。 看了一些回答，的确感觉自己是太过想当然了，但是依然还是想保留一部分看法，说 pc 时代过去了不是很同意，而且见识这一点，虽然我们有墙，但是感觉日本年轻人现在获取信息的渠道要是就靠智能手机和因为 pc 不主流而依然占据相当地位的电视，我觉得绝大部分一般层次的日本人获取到的信息无论质和量都不如国内同层次的年轻人。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f32c6f0d94ec1eaf9f15444b6d29031b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "112 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/444908561"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I/rnVr8Dys9oJEAMaCDYxMTQ3MTQxIIiMtIEGMAU4WkAocgk0NDQ5MDg1NjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1613649722.3890939", "card_id": "Q_442815799", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在 21 世纪，谁是 NBA 中距离最准的球员？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-909d239822484fbe334feeedea0cdfb8_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "111 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/442815799"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I/rnVr8Dys9oJEAMaCDYwNjgxMzU2IKKD7oAGMAA4NkApcgk0NDI4MTU3OTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1613649722.389496", "card_id": "Q_445022887", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 67}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待华南师大附中新学期推出的学生携带手机入校申请表？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/445022887"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/rnVr8Dys9oJEAMaCDYxMTcyNjUyIMORuIEGMAE4nQFAKnIJNDQ1MDIyODg3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1613649722.3898947", "card_id": "Q_440297994", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "作为一个大